quran[43]{c,v,t}:
  13,1,"Alif, Laam, Miim, Raa. ∆äee ko aayeeje deftere nden; jippinaande nden e maa…óa immorde ka Joomi maa ko goonga; kono ko …ďuri …óuu…óude e yim…ďe …ďen …ďe ngooŇč…óintaa."
  13,2,"Ko Alla woni …ďamtu…óo kammuuli …óin doose …óe on nji'ataa. refti O fotondiri ka dow 'Arshi, O elti naange ngeen e lewru ndun: kala majji no doga haa e lajal innaangal. Hino toppitoo fiyaakuuji …óin, Homo fensita aayeeje …óeen belejo'o on njanante kawwroygol e Joomi mon."
  13,3,"Ko KaŇčko woni fontu…óo leydi ndin, O wa…ói e majji pelle e caatli. E kala (noone) e dim…óe, o wa…ói e majje noone …ói…ói resindiray…ói. Homo suddira jemma on √Īalawma on. Wonii e …óuum, maandeeji wonan`de yim…ďe miijitotoo…ďe."
  13,4,"Hino ka leydi tummbe …ďadondir…óe, e gese 'inabu, e remuruuji, e tamarooje dukkin…óe e …óe wonaa …óukkin…óe, he…óe yarniree ndiyam ngootam, Mi…óen …ďurna yoga majji dow yoga ka dakamme. Wonii e …óuum, maandeeji wonan¬īde yim…ďe haqqiloo…ďe."
  13,5,"Si a Ňčal…óay, -haawete-haray ko konngol ma…ď…ďe ngol jojji Ňčal…óude:-haawniinde- ""Eyoo si men wontii mbulmbuldi, mene men wontat e tagoore hesre?"" Ko …ďeen ngoni yeddu…ďe Joomi mun …ďen, ko …ďeen tonngoytee ka daa…óe mun, ko …ďen kadi ngoni yim…ďe Yiite; kam…ďe ko …ďe luttoo…ďe e magge."
  13,6,"He…ďe hawjirane bone on ado mo∆ī∆īere nden. GooŇč…óii wulike ado ma…ď…ďe [lepte] yeruuje majje. Pellet, Joomi maa ko Jom-haforanal wonan`de yim…ďe …ďeen, e too√Īe ma…ď…ďe …óeen. Pellet kadi Joomi maa, ko c…óttu…óo lepte."
  13,7,"∆Āeen heefere…ďe no wi'a: ""Ko ha…óno maande jippiniree e makko immorde ka Joomi makko?"" Anndu ko an ko a jertinoowo, hino woodani yim…ďe kala pewnoowo."
  13,8,"Alla no anndi ko roondotoo kala deyel, e ko renngaaji …óin ustata e ko …ói …ďeydata. Kala huunde ka makko, ko e…ď…ďaa-…óum."
  13,9,"ganndu…óo k owirnii…ói e fee√Īu…ói, maw…óo, toownitii…óo."
  13,10,"Hino fota [ka makko ganndugol] oon cuu…óu…óo konngol e moo…óon, e on pe√Ī√Īin…óo ngol, on cuu…óirat…óo jemma, e on jaltiniroowo √Īalawma."
  13,11,"Hino woodani mo lomtondiroo…ďe yeeso makko e …ďaawo makko, he…ďe ndeenira mo yamiroore Alla. Pellet Alla waylataa ko woni e yim…ďe, haa …ďe mbayla ko woni kon e ma…ď…ďe. Si Alla faandanike yim…ďe bone, alaa yiltoowo mo. Alanaa …ďe gaanin makko gi…óo-heftoowo."
  13,12,"Ko KaŇčko woni kolliray…óo on ma∆īe …óen kulul […óe] e tam∆īinagol [to…ďo]; O fu…ó…óa …óeen duule teddu…óe."
  13,13,"Digge …óeen no senina mo yettugol mo, e maleykaaji …ďen, immorde e kulol makko. o wurta par√Īite …óen, O meminira …óe on mo o muuyi. Kam…ďe he…ďe wennja fii Alla, KaŇčko non ko O sa…ótu…óo nanngal."
  13,14,"Hino woodani oo noddaandu goonga! ∆äiin …ói …ďe noddata ko woori Mo, …ói jaabotaako …ďe e huunde; si wanaa wano fontu…óo newe mun e ndiyam fii yo …óam yotto hunnduko makko, kono …óam wonaani joottotoo-…óam kon (hunnduko). Noddaandu heefere…ďe …ďen wonaani si wonaa e majjere."
  13,15,"Ko Alla woni ko sujjannta, denndaangal ko woni ka kammuuji e la leydi, …óoftaare e waawneede, e …óowdiiji ma…ď…ďe, bimmbi e kiikii…óe."
  13,16,"Maaku: ""Ko hommbo jeyi kammuuji …óiin e leydi ndin?"" Maaku: ""Ko Alla"". Maaku: ""E on njogiti gaanin makko, keedii…ói …ói mbaawanaa ko'e majji nafa wanaa lorra?"" Maaku: ""Hara bum…óo e ji'iiwo no fota? Kaa hara ni…ďe …óen fotay e ndaygu ngu? Kaa …ďe wa…óan Alla kafidii…ďe tagir…ďe wano tagoore makko nde, tagoore nde nanndari …ďe? Maaku: ""Ko Alla woni tak…óo kala huunde, ko KaŇčko woni bajjo, pool…óo""."
  13,17,"O jippinirii ka kammu ndiyam, …óam ili e jooli=caatli =emmbere majjam. Ilol ngol roondii ngufo hummbu-ngo. No e kon ko …ďe ku…ď…ďata yiite e mun fii …óa…ď…ďu …óa…ď…ďugol cu…óaari maa nafa-hoy, ngufo sugu mun. Ko wano nii Alla wa…óirta misal goonga e fenannde. Si ko ngufo ngon, ngo yahray …ďee…ďugol, ammaa ko nafata yim…ďe …ďeen kon, …óum √Īii…ďa ka leydi. Ko wano nii Alla wa…óirta yeruuji …óiin."
  13,18,"Hino woodani …ďeen nootii…ďe Joomi mun mo∆ī∆īere. ∆Āeen …ďe nootaaki Mo, sinno woodaniino …ďe denndaangal ko woni kon ka leydi, e yeru mun won¬īdude e mu'un, …ďe soktorayno(coottorto) …óum. ∆Āeen …óon, no woodani …ďe bon…óum hasboore, jaa∆īorde ma…ď…ďe nden ko Jahannama. Nge bonii nda…ó…óundi."
  13,19,"E ko on ganndu…óo won¬īde ko jippinaa ko e maa…óa immorde ka Joomi maa ko goonga, wa'ata wa on …ďum…óo? Anndu ko waajitotoo, ko joomiraa…ďe-haqqillaaji …ďeen,"
  13,20,"∆Āeen huu…ďnoo…ďe ahadi Alla ndiin, …ďe pirtataa ahodal(hoolaare)."
  13,21,"e …ďeen jokkoo…ďe …óuum ko Alla yamiri yo jokke, he…ďe kula Joomi ma…ď…ďe, he…ďe kula bon¬īde hasboore,"
  13,22,"∆Āeen mu√Ī√Īorii…ďe …óa…ď…ďugol yarluyee Joomi ma…ď…ďe, …ďe √Īii…ďni julde, …ďe nafqii e kon ko min arsiki …ďe, gunndoo e kene, he…ďe du√Īira mo∆ī∆īere ndeen bone on. ∆Āeen …óoon, no woodani …ďe battane galle,"
  13,23,"Aljannaaji √Īii…ďal, he…ďe naata …ói, e …ďeen mo∆ī∆īu…ďe e baabiraa…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďeen, e rew…ďe ma…ď…ďe …ďen, e geyngolji=…ďesnguuji =ma…ď…ďe …óin. Hara Maleykaaji …ói hino naatirana …ďe kala damal:"
  13,24,"""Kisal wonii e mo'on, sabu mu√Īal mon ngal. battane galle …óeen mo∆ī∆īii""."
  13,25,"∆Āeen (non) firtoo…ďe ahadi Alla ndin …ďaawo pi…ďugol ndi, he…ďe ta∆īoo e ko Alla yamiri kon yo jokke, he…ďe mbonna ka leydi, …ďee …óoo, hino woodani …ďe ku…ódi, hino woodani …ďe kadi bon…óum galle."
  13,26,"Alla no ya√Ī√Īana arsike on mo o muuyi, Himo …ďittina. he…ďe mbeltora nguurndam aduna, nguurndam aduna non wonaani ka laakara, si wanaa dakamme-hoy."
  13,27,"∆Āeen yeddu…ďe no mbi'a: ""Ko ha…óno aaya jippinee e makko immorde ka Joomi makko?"" Maaku: ""Alla majjinat tun mo o muuyi, O fewna e makko on tuubu…óo-ruttii"""
  13,28,"∆Āeen gooŇč…óin…ďe, …ďe …ďer…óe mun dee∆īirta jantagol Alla. Ngandee ko jaŇčtagol Alla ngol …ďer…óe …óeen ndee∆īirta."
  13,29,"∆Āeen gooŇč…óii…ďe …ďe ngolli golle mo∆ī∆īe, welo-welo woodanii…ďe e mo∆ī∆īude ruttorde."
  13,30,"Ko wano nii min nulir-maa e mofte - gooŇč…óii mofte goo yawtiino ado majje - fii yo a janngan …ďe nden nde min wahayini e maa…óa, kono he…ďe yedda Yurmetee…óo on. maaku: ""Ko KaŇčko woni Joomi am. dewetee…óo alaa si wanaa KaŇčko. Ko e makko mi fawii, ko ka makko kadi woni ruttorde am""."
  13,31,"Sinno janngeteende na…ďirano pelle …óe, maa leydi ndin seekiraa sabu mayre, maa nde wowliniraa maay…ďe …ďen (harayno ko ndee …óoo). Ko woni, ko Alla woodani fiyaaku on fow. E gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen nganndaanii won¬īde, sinno Alla muuyuno, o fewnatna denndaangal yim…ďe …ďen? Masiibo seeraani no he…ďira yeddu…ďe …ďeen ko …ďe paggitii kon, maa [ngon masiibo] yana takko galle ma…ď…ďe nden haa fodoore Alla nden ara. Pellet Alla firtataa fodoore."
  13,32,"GoŇč…óii nulaa…ďe njalkitanoo ma ado maa…óa. mi mu√Ī√Īanii …ďen yeddu…ďe, refti Mi nanngi …ďe. Ko honno lepte am …óen ngonirnoo!"
  13,33,"E hara ko oon darii…óo e kala woŇčkii ko ki faggitii kon […ďuri hanndude e dewal?...] ∆Āe mba…óanii Alla kafidii- …ói. Maaku: ""Innee-…ói"" Kaa on humpitay mo ko o ngnndaa ka leydi? Kaa ko ko [tun] e konngol? Ko woni, heefer…ďe …ďeen cu…óinanaa ma pewje ma…ď…ďe …óeen, …ďe sakkaa(pala) e laawol ngol. Kala mo Alla majjini, peewnoowo alanaa mo."
  13,34,"Hino woodani …ďe lepte ka nguurndam aduna. Pellet ko lepte laakara …óen …ďuri sattude, alanaa …ďe da…óndoowo (…ďe) e Alla."
  13,35,"Sugu Aljanna mo gooŇč…óu…ďe …ďeen fodaa on: Caati no ila ley makko; √Īaamri makko …ói ko duumii…óum, e …óowdi makko ndin. ∆äuum ko battane …ďen gooŇč…óu…ďe, battane heeferbe non ko Yiite."
  13,36,"∆Āeen …ďe mnn okki deftere ndeen, he…ďe mbeltora …óuum ko jippinaa e maa…óa. No e le∆ī∆īi kon …ďen yeddoo…ďe yoga mayre. Maaku: ""nganndee ko yamiraa-mi, ko nde reway-mi Alla hara mi sirkanaali mo. Ko e makko nodday-mi, ko ka makko kadi woni ruttorde am""."
  13,37,"Ko wano nii min njippiniri nde √Īaawoore (e haala) aarabu. Pellet si a jokkii mbelee…óe ma…ď…ďe …óen …ďaawo nde ganndal ari e maa, alanaa ma gaanin Alla immorde e gi…óo, wanaa da…óndoowo."
  13,38,"GooŇč…óii min nulii nulaa…ďe ado maa, min wa…óani …ďe genndiraa…ďe e geyngol. Haananaa Nulaa…óo nde o addata Aaya, si wanaa e sakkitoore Alla. Hino woodani kala lajal caati.(happu binnda…óo)"
  13,39,"Alla no meha (momta)ko Muuyi o tabatina (ko o wela), ko ka makko yumma defte …óeen woni."
  13,40,"Si minn kolliima yogo e ko min fodi …ďe, maa Mmin hunnu maa (ado mun), anndu ko fawi maa ko yottingol, haasboore nde ko minen fawtii."
  13,41,"E …ďee nji'aani won¬īde mi…óen ngara e leydi ndin, min ustira ndi ka seraaji mayri? Alla no √Īaawa, alaa wurtinoowo √Īaawoore makko nden, ko o yaccii…óo (jaaw…óo)√Īaawoore."
  13,42,"GooŇč…óii …ďen adinoo…ďe …ďe pewjaniino (Annabaa…ďe ma…ď…ďe); ko Alla non pewje …óeen fow keeranii. Homo anndi kala woŇčkii faggitotoo. Arma heefere…ďe …ďeen ngannda ko hommbo battane galle (mo∆ī∆īe) woodani."
  13,43,"Heefer…ďe …ďeen he…ďeo mbi'a: ""wonaa a nulaa…óo"". Maaku: ""Alla yonii seedee hakkunde am e mon, e …ďen jogitii…ďe ganndal deftere ndeen""."
